                      <img alt="" class="image-style-os-slideshow-31-980" height="327" src="//static.hwpi.harvard.edu/files/styles/os_slideshow_3%3A1_980/public/ovpr-test/files/about-home.jpg?m=1515604263&amp;itok=u5rVn95k" width="980"/>
                     </a>
                     <div class="caption slide-copy">
                      <h2>
                       <a href="https://vpr.harvard.edu/pages/about">
                        About VPR
                       </a>
                      </h2>
                      <p>
                       <a href="https://vpr.harvard.edu/pages/about">
                        Who we are and what we do.
                       </a>
                      </p>
                     </div>
                    </li>
                   </ul>
