            <section class="block block-boxes block-boxes-os_boxes_html" delta="1550771683" id="block-boxes-1550771683" module="boxes">
             <div class="block-inner clearfix">
              <h2 class="block-title" ng-non-bindable="">
               Update on NIH Reporting Requirements
              </h2>
              <div class="block-content content" ng-non-bindable="">
               <div class="boxes-box" id="boxes-box-1550771683">
                <div class="boxes-box-content">
                 <p>
                  In response to recent communications with the NIH and other federal agencies, including the
                  <a href="https://www.nih.gov/about-nih/who-we-are/nih-director/statements/statement-protecting-integrity-us-biomedical-research" title="">
                   statement
                  </a>
                  from NIH Director Dr. Francis Collins, we have developed the following
                  <a href="https://vpr.harvard.edu/files/ovpr-test/files/guidance_on_reporting_and_disclosure_requirements.pdf">
                   Guidance
                  </a>
                  and
                  <a href="https://vpr.harvard.edu/files/ovpr-test/files/faq_reporting_and_disclosure_guidance.pdf">
                   FAQs
                  </a>
                  to assist faculty and administrators with federal reporting and disclosure requirements pertaining to Outside Activities, Financial Conflict of Interest, and Current and Pending and/or Other Support.
                 </p>
                </div>
               </div>
              </div>
             </div>
            </section>
